      *                  * Test se default da utilizzare               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-tip-mps        not  = spaces
                     go to acc-tip-mps-def-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Utilizzo del default                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-def-tip-mps        to   w-tes-tip-mps          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad uscita                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     acc-tip-mps-def-900.
       acc-tip-mps-def-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
