      *                  * il codice prodotto per il cliente           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     prn-liv-det-600.
      *
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      w-prm-pst-chm-lfl (6)
                                          to   p-car                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
